SUMMARY:Deadline: Wikimedia Conference Fund
DESCRIPTION:Wikimedia Foundation grants supporting the organisation of loca
 l\, regional and thematic conferences that bring Wikimedians together for 
 knowledge sharing\, skill development and professional networking. Two rou
 nds per year. Round 1 deadline: 31 August 2026. Round 2 deadline: 1 Februa
 ry 2027. ELIGIBILITY: groups\, organisations and Wikimedia affiliates\; in
 dividuals may apply via a fiscal sponsor.\n\nOrganisation: Wikimedia Found
 ation\nLocation: Worldwide (subject to legal eligibility by country)\nAwar
 d: From USD 10\,000 per grant (no preset upper cap stated). No application
  fee.\nDuration: Project-based. Processing approximately 3 months from sub
 mission to decision\, plus 2-3 weeks for finalisation before disbursement.
 \n\nMore: https://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/Grants:Conference
URL:https://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/Grants:Conference
LOCATION:Worldwide (subject to legal eligibility by country)
